                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17901027-37-defend509 t17901027-37-punish194"></join>
               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. Justice HEATH.</p>
